New calibers for bullets can be bought in the store, each with different effects.

Slowness Caliber:
Cost (16 bullets): 24 Iron
Bullet Trail: Gray
Effect: Slowness 2 on hit

Harming Caliber:
Cost (16 bullets): 8 Gold
Bullet Trail: Dark Red
Effect: 20% more damage per bullet

Tracking Caliber:
Cost (16 bullets): 2 Emeralds
Bullet Trail: Bright Red
Effect: Points your compass toward the last enemy hit for 10 nonstackable seconds.

Phantom Caliber:
Cost (16 bullets): 4 Tags (getting a kill gives you one tag)
Bullet Trail: None
Effect: Your bullets have no trail
